{"tid":672574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Bill Gates瘋狂恥笑特朗普：唔識分HIV同HPV; 走人後搭直升機折返攞威","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T03:35:30.000Z","uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"038994445b08568fe31d1a80e806754e7147a706","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180518/58210072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58210072&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=396703ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58210072&h=0a44db04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180518/58210072</a><br />\n<br />\n 美國電視台MSNBC周四晚播出獨家片段，披露微軟創辦人蓋茨（Bill Gates）兩次見美國總統特朗普的印象：特朗普分不清HIV（愛滋病毒）和HPV（人類乳頭瘤病毒），但就難忘蓋茨22歲女兒。<br />\n<br />\n片段錄自蓋茨夫妻名下慈善基金會一次答問會，蓋茨說特朗普當選後，兩人於2016年12月及2017年3月有兩面之緣，原應討論創科發展，結果話題卻繞到性病上：「他兩次問到HIV和HPV的分別，我有幸向他解釋兩者很少會被混淆。」蓋茨說時表情認真，但已惹來哄堂大笑。<br />\n<br />\nHIV全名為人類免疫力缺乏病毒，經體液入侵人體，攻擊抗疫的T4細胞；HPV則有多種類，經皮膚、性接觸甚至母體傳染，可致俗稱「椰菜花」的性病，甚至子宮頸癌。<br />\n<br />\n此前，特朗普已在佛州某場合見過蓋茨女兒珍妮花，「初次見面他就對我家女兒相貌那麼熟悉，實在令我吃驚，（妻子）梅琳達也不太高興」。蓋茨又轉述女兒見聞，指特朗普當日跟她閒聊後一度離開，20分鐘乘直升機折返，「只為增加進場氣勢」。"},{"pid":"552e997b9f69969058e0245868b1f552a683c958","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"&quot;When I walked in, his first sentence kind of threw me off,&quot; Gates said. &quot;He said, 'Trump hears that you don't like what Trump is doing.' And I thought, 'Wow, but you're Trump!' <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/bill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=315f1402\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.businessinsider.com/bill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寶寶心裡苦，但寶寶不說"},{"pid":"3259c2bb4fedf922d2c8578e42ed024492179597","tid":672574,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"552e997b9f69969058e0245868b1f552a683c958","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"&quot;When I walked in, his first sentence kind of threw me off,&quot; Gates said. &quot;He said, 'Trump hears that you don't like what Trump is doing.' And I thought, 'Wow, but you're Trump!' <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/bill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=315f1402\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.businessinsider.com/bill-gates-donald-trump-speaks-in-third-person-leaked-video-2018-5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寶寶心裡苦，但寶寶不說"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"鄺俊宇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特朗普"},{"pid":"01598635bf6468d23dbf9266fa73a3ca8e2dbcf6","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 標基畀侵侵撚左狗都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 侵侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349f850004a54dff84bd5d958c246fc834b32797","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d472fa5f0b8f8f320322472e6c66b3341042c6f5","tid":672574,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"HIV HPV HSV 是旦一樣都死啦"},{"pid":"9afbab561c9f70ef10428a0b7cf9b09f471b1b59","tid":672574,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9da25f92232e2948715f29f85b5aebf435c605d5","tid":672574,"uid":84392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76783f4c4c2333f4991130e3a9150231b2c5bd24","tid":672574,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"915dfded3cf09c05630dff3323261c2ab97c376e","tid":672574,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dY7byG1YGwg?t=28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdY7byG1YGwg%3Ft%3D28&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=74a4e46c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dY7byG1YGwg?t=28</a>"},{"pid":"8e395b218a24f2684e62104d05af5a173535c1ff","tid":672574,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"侵諗住講下笑咁搞下氣氛，點知Bill Gates又會當真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBill Gates真係比侵撚狗咁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=